metadata.name: toast is done is toast #1/20
metadata.description:
Originally published on the 12th of December 2002 on deviantart, this animation shows an eternal circle of toast being toasted.

To celebrate its 20 year anniversary, this breakfast mantra will now live forever in the blockchain.

...is done is toast is done is toast is done is toast is done is toast is done is toast is done is toast is done is toast is done...
